      "date": "2016-04-29 06:56:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n\"Di, it looks like replay-single failed twice with your debug patch applied. Do the test results have the information you need to fix this problem?\"\n\nAndreas: I checked those failures, but it seems my guessing is not correct. In those failure logs, it seems lookup (in sys_unlink) failed with ENOENT somehow during DNE recovery.  I had thought this is related with slave stripes revalidation, but unfortunately the debug patch did not catch the failure there. I will continue working on this failure this weekend, sorry for the delay.",
